the extreme left and right in El Salvador bring neither liberation
nor order, they bring suffering, terror and death. We condemn these
acts of violence.''
   He said attacks were the work of terrorists and murderers, and
``we vigorously denounce them. Violence only serves the interests
of extremists who oppose democracy and national reconciliation.''
