hospital had no comment on his condition.
   At El Salvador's embassy, press aide Eduardo Torres said that
Duarte arrived in Washington last Friday and ``he's in bad shape.''
   The tenative plan is for Duarte to remain at the hospital for
about two more days and then return to El Salvador, said the
administration official, who asked not to be identified.
